Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.17,0:22:08.51,EDJP,,25,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\an7\blur8\bord1.7}まだ通り風が　時折り肌を刺す朝に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.51,0:22:15.42,EDJP,,25,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\an7\blur8\bord1.7}雪解けた　瞼の暗闇を抜け
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.42,0:22:19.78,EDJP,,25,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\an7\blur8\bord1.7}今「何が見える？」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.78,0:22:25.00,EDJP,,25,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\an7\blur8\bord1.7}響かせた　応えは知れず
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.00,0:22:30.53,EDJP,,25,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\an7\blur8\bord1.7}想い出の中　笑いかける
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.53,0:22:36.42,EDJP,,25,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\an7\blur8\bord1.7}あの日の貴方も同じ　それは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.42,0:22:42.54,EDJP,,25,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\an7\blur8\bord1.7}行き場もなく　ただ風に舞う
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.36,0:22:46.76,EDJP,,25,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\an7\blur8\bord1.7}花「いざや。」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.76,0:22:54.00,EDJP,,25,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\an7\blur8\bord1.7}春は咲き　涙に花弁
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.00,0:23:03.95,EDJP,,25,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\an7\blur8\bord1.7}今さら悲哀など　疾うに果てたまま
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.95,0:23:09.18,EDJP,,25,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\an7\blur8\bord1.7}過ぎ去れば　また季は巡り
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.18,0:23:14.57,EDJP,,25,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\an7\blur8\bord1.7}遠く晴れた　それに紛れる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.57,0:23:20.47,EDJP,,25,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\an7\blur8\bord1.7}憶いだけが　共に掠れず
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.47,0:23:25.38,EDJP,,25,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\an7\blur8\bord1.7}その声が　春を告げる
Dialogue: 1,0:21:59.17,0:22:08.51,EDCN,,25,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\an7\blur8\bord1.7}晓风拂帘幔 时复透骨寒
Dialogue: 1,0:22:08.51,0:22:15.42,EDCN,,25,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\an7\blur8\bord1.7}雪融眸初启 长夜尽阑珊
Dialogue: 1,0:22:15.42,0:22:19.78,EDCN,,25,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\an7\blur8\bord1.7}君兮 君兮 今何见
Dialogue: 1,0:22:19.78,0:22:25.00,EDCN,,25,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\an7\blur8\bord1.7}清响留空寂 回音不可寻
Dialogue: 1,0:22:25.00,0:22:30.53,EDCN,,25,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\an7\blur8\bord1.7}繁花照旧影 梦深复逢君
Dialogue: 1,0:22:30.53,0:22:36.42,EDCN,,25,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\an7\blur8\bord1.7}昔日同笑语 共折柳色新
Dialogue: 1,0:22:36.42,0:22:42.54,EDCN,,25,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\an7\blur8\bord1.7}而今无所寄 飘摇似飞英
Dialogue: 1,0:22:43.36,0:22:46.76,EDCN,,25,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\an7\blur8\bord1.7}花兮 花兮 今曷归
Dialogue: 1,0:22:46.76,0:22:54.00,EDCN,,25,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\an7\blur8\bord1.7}春来胭脂雪 泪雨落满枝
Dialogue: 1,0:22:54.00,0:23:03.95,EDCN,,25,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\an7\blur8\bord1.7}二三愁绪没 几处蝶影稀
Dialogue: 1,0:23:03.95,0:23:09.18,EDCN,,25,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\an7\blur8\bord1.7}雪霁层云散 劫尽韶光开
Dialogue: 1,0:23:09.18,0:23:14.57,EDCN,,25,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\an7\blur8\bord1.7}四时驹重驭 独此忆悬幡
Dialogue: 1,0:23:14.57,0:23:20.47,EDCN,,25,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\an7\blur8\bord1.7}悠思萦香绕 不与春秋老
Dialogue: 1,0:23:20.47,0:23:25.38,EDCN,,25,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\an7\blur8\bord1.7}余音诉未尽 声声唤春潮
